{
  "stem": "11797.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But thank goodness that my-- this lady took care of my youngest brother, who was a year old.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She took care of him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because she-- I was told later on she was not able to have children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she was quite happy that she had came into a ready-made family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They must have married in '35.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they were only married a few years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather remained in my house, you know, until he passed away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She allowed, my stepmother, allowed that, yeah, like a-- like a-- she was a very good person.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather died-- I don't know, maybe it was about 1938, something-- right before the war, he passed away. '37-- I can't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know he-- I was about 12 or 13 years when he passed away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to take me every night to temple, you know, and say Kaddish, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kaddish?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, tremendously.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was so broken up, you know, when he died, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I felt like, like the world came apart, like everything fell on me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I've-- I was very close to my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A lot of things, you know, he did that made me laugh-- and sometimes made me cry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like one time, when I came back from school and there was a-- he saw me one time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was more in the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he saw me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I went in, I had $0.10 in my pocket, 10 [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I walked into a store to buy a piece of sausage, non-Jewish sausage.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it smelled so nice, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was stupid, you know, because-- for doing that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He caught me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And all the way home, he, he me in my grabbed my ear.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
